## User is customer of author condition

**User is customer of author**Â condition checks if the current user has purchased a particular product from the author of the current post. In case of subscriptions, it checks if there is an active subscription.

When applying a condition, you can optionally input the Author ID. If no Author ID is provided, the condition references current post author.

## Example

Unlock content posted by a specific user, if you buy a subscription from them.
